### Gamification Engine API - Users Endpoints
### Base URL: https://localhost:7000

### Get complete user state
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/state
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user points for all categories
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/points
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user points for specific category
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/points/xp
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user badges
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/badges
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user trophies
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/trophies
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user current level for specific category
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/levels/xp
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user current levels for all categories
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/levels
Accept: application/json

###

### Get user reward history
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user123/rewards/history?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### Test with different user IDs
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/user456/state
Accept: application/json

###

### Test with non-existent user (should return empty state)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users/nonexistent/state
Accept: application/json

###

### Get summarized list of all users (paginated)
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### Get summarized list of all users with default pagination
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users
Accept: application/json

###

### Test pagination with different page sizes
GET https://localhost:7000/api/users?page=2&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###